NOTE ON THE MEASUREMENT CORPUS

This license covers the APEX measurement harness, scripts, and paper in this
repository. It does NOT cover the third-party libraries that the build scripts
fetch and compile. Those libraries are downloaded at build time from their
upstream repositories (see evalkit/corpus_manifest.csv) and remain under their
own respective licenses (zlib, MIT, BSD, public-domain, and similar permissive
terms). No third-party source is vendored in this repository.
